  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}Wh-What? There's someone else here?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}W-We gotta hide![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
