  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 0 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}I know.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}No, I'm not! I'm just a little nervous, that's all![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}I mean, can you blame me? Everyone has something they're afraid of. This is a totally normal reaction.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 0 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}Well, now that I think about it, that could've just been someone else from our group. So hearing footsteps isn't a big deal, maybe?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 1 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 1 25 25}Haha, there's nothing to be afraid of, right? Hahaha... Why am I laughing?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}O-Of course I don't.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 0 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}We already know it's not a ghost.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 2 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 2 25 25}And besides, I'm not that afraid of—[cr][n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Ahhh![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}M-My phone!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Why now!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 6 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}And of course it's just spam.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}I mean, that would freak most people out, right?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}C'mon! The thing just rang out of nowhere![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="SEL_011_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I get that.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}You get scared so easily.]]></Option>
