    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 51 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 3 25 25}All right, fine, I'm a chicken. Happy?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
